    <abstract id="aspace_cfbcbf40f6b2e1e27cee0c66d7c2e9cc" label="Abstract">This collection contains the personal correspondence of Cyrus Mason, 1798-1865. The letters mainly cover personal matters such as religion, the birth of a daughter, and finances.</abstract>
